data.description:
Realtors Welcome!
Southern Charm! Beautiful Custom Colonial Style Home with Unique features. Located in a small quant all custom built homes gated community. Family and Friends gather here! Spacious split 4 bdrm, 3 full baths found upstairs for plenty of personal space. 2 1/2 baths located on lower level (including pool bath) Master Bedroom features fireplace, bathroom with huge steam shower, heated jetted jacuzzi tub. Master Jr Suite includes private full bath. Wood floors and lovely southern charm trim work and moulding through out entire home. 1yr old Samsung wifi washer and dryer. Enjoy making memories in the gorgeous Huge kitchen with plenty of seating, beautiful brick floors and windows, new stone island and counter tops, all stainless steal appliances. Watch your favorite sports in your own personal bar and game room. Cozy up on winter nights to fireplace in your living room or master bedroom! Large cook outs, games, fun to be had in this oversized pool and yard featuring Childs playground. This one of a kind beauty is located within both walking distance and less than 3 miles radius of tons shopping, restaurants, including Westfield Mall! 15 min to downtown Tampa Bay areas, 25 min to Busch Gardens, Adventure Island, 45 min to Disney and more, 45 min to our World Renowned beaches. Don't miss this one!
